WEBVTT

00:00.007 --> 00:05.007


00:47.707 --> 00:53.627
<b><i>If you do not wish for this cat to die,{ep03@15:50} 
then bring me a human.{ep03@15:53}</i></b>

00:58.717 --> 01:00.877
<b><i>All life is equally meaningless.</i></b>

01:01.687 --> 01:03.127
<b><i>So why am I running</i></b>

01:03.997 --> 01:05.807
<b><i>over a mere cat?</i></b>

01:05.807 --> 01:07.387
<b><i>Why am I searching for a human?</i></b>

01:10.967 --> 01:12.887
<b><i>To save Meowy?</i></b>

01:17.777 --> 01:19.897
<b><i>How ridiculous.</i></b>

01:24.567 --> 01:26.587
<b><i>I like blood.</i></b>

01:26.587 --> 01:28.917
<b><i>I like its taste and scent.</i></b>

01:28.917 --> 01:30.677
<b><i>I like how you feel death through it.</i></b>

01:31.657 --> 01:32.977
<b><i>Also...</i></b>

01:32.977 --> 01:36.117
<b><i>I recently realized something else for the first time.</i></b>

01:37.417 --> 01:39.287
<b><i>Blood is warm</i></b>

01:40.587 --> 01:42.387
<b><i>and feels nice.</i></b>

02:04.757 --> 02:06.647
<b>Why did you save me?</b>

02:07.827 --> 02:10.097
<b>I was trying to get you killed.</b>

02:22.437 --> 02:24.967
<b>How ridiculous.</b>

02:34.127 --> 02:36.467
<b>I apologize for deceiving you.</b>

02:36.467 --> 02:38.977
<b>Meowy is safe.</b>

02:39.607 --> 02:41.527
<b>I'll let you touch my boobs.</b>

02:51.267 --> 02:59.877
<b>Yeaaaaaaaaaaah!</b>

02:51.267 --> 02:59.037
<b>Yeaaaaaaaaaaah!</b>

02:57.827 --> 02:59.877
<b>Yeaaaaaaaaouch!</b>

02:59.867 --> 03:01.867
<b>Oh, fuck!</b>

03:01.867 --> 03:03.627
<b>Fuck!</b>

03:04.637 --> 03:05.877
<b>Shit!</b>

03:31.637 --> 03:32.817
<b>Can you stand?</b>

03:33.437 --> 03:35.237
<b>I can't move a muscle.</b>

03:35.807 --> 03:37.987
<b>Take Meowy and run.</b>

03:47.667 --> 03:50.297
<b>The chainsaws aren't coming out!</b>

03:52.177 --> 03:54.027
<b><i>Guess I don't have enough blood.</i></b>

03:57.387 --> 04:00.217
<b>I'd finally found him,</b>

04:00.727 --> 04:04.347
<b>and then you went ahead and killed Batty.{she has a nickname for the bat devil}</b>

04:04.347 --> 04:07.237
<b>He was my man!</b>

04:09.367 --> 04:13.637
<b>Well, now that I look a little closer,
 you've got a cute face.</b>

04:14.117 --> 04:17.737
<b>For that, I'll let you off this time.</b>

04:18.807 --> 04:20.237
<b>What about those two?</b>

04:23.557 --> 04:24.997
<b>I'm killing them.</b>

04:30.987 --> 04:32.837
<b>Fine, then die.{would this be nicer as "Okay. Then die." or "Okay then. Die"? or "Okay. Die then."}</b>

05:08.087 --> 05:10.487
<b>He's doing all this fighting,</b>

05:11.997 --> 05:14.087
<b>just so he can feel up some boobs?</b>

05:29.637 --> 05:31.267
<b>Are you kidding me?</b>

05:31.267 --> 05:35.277
<b>This little puppy really managed to kill Batty?</b>

05:38.047 --> 05:43.047
<b>He and I had a dream to eat all humans.</b>

05:43.577 --> 05:47.037
<b>It was a crazy, but lofty and noble dream.</b>

05:47.297 --> 05:50.797
<b>And a single puppy destroyed that.</b>

05:51.197 --> 05:53.917
<b>It's a shame to kill a face that nice,</b>

05:54.747 --> 05:56.297
<b>but I'm going to anyway.</b>

05:58.217 --> 06:00.547
<b>You want me to die before I get to touch boobs?</b>

06:00.547 --> 06:02.457
<b>Boring!</b>

06:02.457 --> 06:06.087
<b>Getting killed by someone with such lowly desires.</b>

06:06.087 --> 06:08.807
<b>Poor Batty.</b>

06:10.067 --> 06:12.227
<b><i>How ridiculous.{from earlier}{see previous same line}</i></b>

06:14.077 --> 06:16.147
<b><i>You're the only one here who's not taking this seriously.{ep02@16:26}</i></b>

06:38.767 --> 06:43.337
<b>Why does everyone
 have to look down on my goals?!</b>

06:43.337 --> 06:44.847
<b>Revenge,</b>

06:44.847 --> 06:46.597
<b>protecting family,</b>

06:46.597 --> 06:48.097
<b>saving a cat,</b>

06:48.097 --> 06:50.097
<b>or whatever else.</b>

06:50.097 --> 06:53.217
<b>Must be nice to have admirable dreams, huh!</b>

06:53.217 --> 06:56.147
<b>Let's have a battle of dreams, then! How about it?!</b>

06:56.147 --> 06:58.987
<b>If I manage to kill you,</b>

06:58.987 --> 07:02.607
<b>then that means your dream is below feeling up boobs!</b>

07:02.607 --> 07:04.527
<b>That's some cute barking.</b>

07:04.527 --> 07:06.917
<b>The smaller the dog, the louder the bark!{tlc: she actually voices out the barks here with "wan wan wan wan" so maybe end this line before that and time "woof woof woof woof" to it}{eh, I think repeating it 4 times feels kinda weird in english; 3 would be a bit more natural, but then it has a weird contrast with the audio...}</b>

07:06.917 --> 07:10.247
<b>Fine, then! I'm going to eat you!</b>

07:11.207 --> 07:12.367
<b>Do it, then!</b>

07:12.367 --> 07:16.927
<b>If you can win this battle of dreams!</b>

07:51.907 --> 07:53.497
<b><i>He's a devil...</i></b>

08:32.157 --> 08:35.087
<b>Yummy, yummy!</b>

08:41.057 --> 08:41.837
<b>Yip.{what does the fox say...}</b>

08:50.637 --> 08:53.067
<b>This is the Leech Devil.</b>

08:53.067 --> 08:54.847
<b>May I swallow?</b>

08:55.207 --> 08:56.047
<b>You may.</b>

09:12.607 --> 09:14.787
<b>The Leech Devil has been eliminated.</b>

09:15.167 --> 09:18.157
<b>Newbies, assist any survivors and evacuate the civilians.</b>

09:18.157 --> 09:19.117
<b>Yessir!</b>

09:18.157 --> 09:19.117
<b>Yessir!</b>

09:19.127 --> 09:22.797
<b>Himeno, keep watch for any other devils.</b>

09:22.797 --> 09:23.617
<b>Sure!</b>

09:29.537 --> 09:31.997
<b>You and the Blood Fiend
 are coming in for questioning.</b>

09:33.267 --> 09:34.767
<b>What about Meowy?</b>

09:40.547 --> 09:43.667
<b>Send the cat to a vet for a check-up.</b>

09:57.377 --> 10:00.757
<b>We picked up your arm.</b>

10:01.807 --> 10:04.037
<b>They say it reattached during a transfusion.</b>

10:04.847 --> 10:06.967
<b>You really are like a devil.</b>

10:08.417 --> 10:11.297
<b>You were being friendly with a devil, too.</b>

10:11.707 --> 10:13.247
<b>I saw that.</b>

10:15.057 --> 10:17.557
<b>You really don't know anything.</b>

10:17.847 --> 10:21.827
<b>A devil hunter makes a contract with a devil
 so they can fight other devils.</b>

10:23.307 --> 10:25.977
<b>I have contract with the Fox Devil.</b>

10:25.977 --> 10:30.687
<b>The terms are that in return for its power,
 it gets to eat a part of my body.</b>

10:31.437 --> 10:33.237
<b>This time I gave it some skin.</b>

10:35.067 --> 10:36.077
<b>Sounds painful.</b>

10:37.277 --> 10:39.857
<b>Devils constantly seek the death of humans.</b>

10:40.427 --> 10:42.497
<b>And fiends are no different.</b>

10:44.017 --> 10:46.377
<b>Power's a good person.</b>

10:49.147 --> 10:54.277
<b>We saw the two of you go outside the patrol area on security cameras.</b>

