10:54.887 --> 10:57.887


11:02.207 --> 11:05.817
<b>You were almost killed
 by the Blood Fiend, weren't you?</b>

11:06.377 --> 11:11.067
<b>I don't know why, but you're taking a devil's side again.</b>

11:11.637 --> 11:14.817
<b>I don't really remember what happened.</b>

11:18.417 --> 11:22.267
<b><i>My daughter wants to see
 the chainsaw person to thank him.{I didn't use "chainsaw man" because it looks too much like the title, while the expression is more haphazard}</i></b>

11:22.267 --> 11:23.537
<b><i>Thank you!</i></b>

11:24.197 --> 11:28.107
<b><i>At the office, a devil said
 "You wanna get eaten?!", so I ran.{referencing ep03@18:32}</i></b>

11:28.107 --> 11:30.577
<b><i>But he was in a Public Safety Bureau uniform.</i></b>

11:30.577 --> 11:32.267
<b><i>So I wanted to thank him.</i></b>

11:32.957 --> 11:35.307
<b><i>He went, "I don't give a shit about some dude!"{lmao}</i></b>

11:35.307 --> 11:37.407
<b><i>He cut through the car with me in it.</i></b>

11:37.407 --> 11:39.597
<b><i>A devil with a chainsaw in his head...</i></b>

11:43.277 --> 11:46.707
<b>If I were to investigate more thoroughly
 and report it to the higher-ups,</b>

11:46.707 --> 11:50.147
<b>both you and the Blood Fiend would be disposed of.</b>

11:50.937 --> 11:52.857
<b>But nobody died.</b>

11:53.207 --> 11:57.367
<b>So if you accept one condition,
 I'll let it slide this time.</b>

11:57.747 --> 11:58.707
<b>Huh?</b>

12:02.247 --> 12:04.877
<b>You have to take my advice seriously and follow it.</b>

12:05.427 --> 12:08.127
<b>You're a stupid brat with no morals.</b>

12:08.457 --> 12:12.887
<b>I'm your senior in the Bureau,
 and I always strive to do what is just and moral.</b>

12:13.157 --> 12:17.387
<b>So if you do as I say, you'll be able
 to protect your current way of life.</b>

12:20.317 --> 12:21.437
<b>So?</b>

12:21.437 --> 12:22.887
<b>I want to hear you agreeing.</b>

12:25.497 --> 12:28.397
<b>Sure. I'll think about it.</b>

12:30.037 --> 12:31.897
<b>Leave it to me.</b>

12:31.897 --> 12:35.477
<b>I don't have some lofty goal like the rest of you.</b>

12:35.477 --> 12:37.967
<b>I've only got my cheap dream.</b>

12:38.677 --> 12:42.657
<b>But I'll go at it as seriously as you, okay?</b>

12:43.297 --> 12:45.917
<b>You can expect good things from me.</b>

12:49.687 --> 12:52.167
<b>For now, learn to speak a bit more politely.</b>

12:52.507 --> 12:55.707
<b>Sure, I'll think about that, too.</b>

13:02.027 --> 13:05.057
<b>See? I'm innocent.</b>

13:07.517 --> 13:10.437
<b>Now that that's settled, take these off!</b>

13:10.687 --> 13:13.147
<b>You sure about this?</b>

13:13.147 --> 13:16.467
<b>One day, when this cute fiend murders someone,</b>

13:16.467 --> 13:19.197
<b>it'll be on your head for letting her off, Aki.</b>

13:19.547 --> 13:21.907
<b>We're devil hunters.</b>

13:21.907 --> 13:23.607
<b>Devil or fiend,</b>

13:23.607 --> 13:26.457
<b>we use anything we can.</b>

13:26.887 --> 13:28.457
<b>But they are still the enemy.</b>

13:28.457 --> 13:30.587
<b>We're merely using them.</b>

13:31.217 --> 13:33.717
<b>I'm not making friends with them.</b>

14:05.877 --> 14:07.037
<b>Come in.</b>

14:07.307 --> 14:08.547
<b>Excuse me.</b>

14:17.007 --> 14:21.557
<b>{fading in}They said they didn't realize
 they'd gone outside the patrol area,</b>

14:21.947 --> 14:25.797
<b>and they found a house
 where a "super-evil" devil lived.{he's kinda quoting and using casual wording like "super evil" that he'd never normally say as his own words, especially in front of Makina}</b>

14:25.797 --> 14:28.557
<b>And that's how they encountered the Bat Devil.</b>

14:28.957 --> 14:32.357
<b>Denji used his chainsaws to defeat the Bat Devil,</b>

14:32.357 --> 14:35.287
<b>but was then attacked by the Leech Devil.</b>

14:35.287 --> 14:37.567
<b>We of the Fourth Division eliminated the latter.</b>

14:38.047 --> 14:42.697
<b>No Gun flesh was found in the Bat or Leech.{talking about pieces of the body of the Gun Devil}</b>

14:43.087 --> 14:44.587
<b>That concludes my report.</b>

14:47.617 --> 14:49.207
<b>Good work.</b>

14:49.627 --> 14:56.837
<b>I'm surprised Denji and Power
 ended up that far out without realizing it.</b>

14:57.337 --> 15:00.087
<b>They're both stupid to a degree that defies belief.</b>

15:00.347 --> 15:04.847
<b>Exiting the patrol area is a violation.</b>

15:04.847 --> 15:07.397
<b>No one died,</b>

15:07.397 --> 15:12.037
<b>and we managed to eliminate two devils,
 so I thought we could overlook it this time.</b>

15:17.827 --> 15:19.227
<b>Very well.</b>

15:19.827 --> 15:22.237
<b>Then, allow me to excuse myself.{what's a polite way to say "I'm leaving then, bye"?}</b>

15:23.187 --> 15:26.627
<b>Have you become a bit more open-minded about this, Hayakawa?</b>

15:28.047 --> 15:31.997
<b>Maybe it's an effect of living with Denji?</b>

15:32.477 --> 15:33.367
<b>Impossible.</b>

15:34.307 --> 15:37.387
<b>I have not changed at all.{timing: includes the "ore wa" after the pause. we may do something with it, if people feel it stands weird}</b>

