17:09.057 --> 17:11.227
<b>Where'd he go?{not sure if I'm making out Denji's yawn correctly, confirm with TLC and/or CCs}</b>

17:37.597 --> 17:38.997
<b>What's for lunch?</b>

17:39.767 --> 17:40.997
<b>Curry.</b>

17:40.997 --> 17:42.067
<b>Dope.</b>

17:45.657 --> 17:47.967
<b>What's that? A devil?</b>

17:52.967 --> 17:54.977
<b>Hey! Hey! Hey!</b>

17:54.977 --> 17:57.987
<b>This dwelling is very cramped!</b>

18:01.557 --> 18:06.237
<b>I'd like you to give Power a room at your place.</b>

18:06.237 --> 18:11.237
<b>You can be a good leash for those two.</b>

18:11.237 --> 18:14.867
<b>{background}Ah! Hold on, Meowy!</b>

18:11.237 --> 18:14.867
<b>Why do you keep sending
 the troublemakers to live with me?!</b>

18:14.867 --> 18:19.367
<b>It's because I can't trust anyone more than you, Hayakawa.</b>

18:14.867 --> 18:19.367
<b>{background}{can't make it out here maybe TLC or CCs can bring something}</b>

18:19.367 --> 18:20.407
<b>It's mine now!</b>

18:20.407 --> 18:22.627
<b>That's my ultimate one!</b>

18:23.247 --> 18:25.377
<b>{background}{can't make it out here maybe TLC or CCs can bring something}</b>

18:23.247 --> 18:25.377
<b>Oh. Understood.</b>

18:25.787 --> 18:28.827
<b>And we can't just have her
 live at the office forever.</b>

18:30.157 --> 18:30.847
<b>Yes.</b>

18:32.447 --> 18:33.387
<b>Right.</b>

18:34.517 --> 18:39.647
<b>Don't worry. Power said she could be a good girl.</b>

18:40.087 --> 18:41.357
<b><i>It'll be alright.</i></b>

18:43.647 --> 18:44.897
<b>I hate vegetables!</b>

18:45.247 --> 18:46.407
<b>Begone!</b>

18:46.407 --> 18:47.327
<b>Ah! Carrot!</b>

18:48.447 --> 18:50.007
<b>Don't throw vegetables!</b>

18:50.007 --> 18:54.157
<b>Hey! Don't you think you're being rude
 to the farmers who grew this?!</b>

18:54.157 --> 18:55.467
<b>Devil!</b>

18:57.157 --> 18:58.157
<b>The toilet?</b>

18:58.587 --> 19:00.787
<b>I only flush shit on occasion.</b>

19:01.057 --> 19:02.047
<b>Flush it!</b>

19:02.047 --> 19:03.417
<b>It stinks!</b>

19:03.737 --> 19:05.627
<b>I only take baths on occasion.</b>

19:05.627 --> 19:06.907
<b>Bathe!</b>

19:06.907 --> 19:08.297
<b>You stink!</b>

19:08.597 --> 19:10.557
<b>What's wrong with you two?</b>

19:10.557 --> 19:12.997
<b>Humans are so sensitive,</b>

19:12.997 --> 19:14.297
<b>right, Meowy?</b>

19:23.807 --> 19:27.317
<b>That bitch just walked in
 and screwed everything up.{now you know how hayakawa felt, lol}</b>

19:27.587 --> 19:30.067
<b>That devil can't even flush her shit!</b>

19:30.067 --> 19:32.287
<b>And she throws away her veggies.</b>

19:32.287 --> 19:33.567
<b>Hey, you!</b>

19:34.677 --> 19:36.327
<b>Hey, Shit Devil!</b>

19:36.327 --> 19:39.327
<b>Your shit is so sticky I can't get it off!</b>

19:44.297 --> 19:45.007
<b>What?{timing is way off}</b>

19:46.167 --> 19:48.157
<b>I promised you, right?</b>

19:48.157 --> 19:50.687
<b>I'll let you feel up my boobs.</b>

19:50.687 --> 19:51.967
<b>Do it!</b>

20:07.687 --> 20:09.257
<b>Come on! What's wrong?</b>

20:09.257 --> 20:10.797
<b>I know you're excited.</b>

20:10.797 --> 20:12.187
<b>Come on!</b>

20:17.757 --> 20:19.447
<b>There's just one condition.</b>

20:20.717 --> 20:24.077
<b>You get three squeezes.</b>

20:24.737 --> 20:26.077
<b>Three squeezes...</b>

20:27.027 --> 20:29.677
<b>One for saving Meowy.</b>

20:29.677 --> 20:32.437
<b>One for killing Bat.</b>

20:32.437 --> 20:36.927
<b>And one for covering for me
 with Topknot.{I'm guessing it's her nickname for Hayakawa} That makes three.</b>

20:37.427 --> 20:39.937
<b>At first, I was lying about letting you touch them,</b>

20:40.277 --> 20:43.427
<b>but to thank you for what you did
 for me, I'll give you three squeezes.</b>

20:43.427 --> 20:45.487
<b>Squeeze with gratitude in your heart.</b>

20:52.817 --> 20:54.177
<b>My angel!{not sure if it's out loud}</b>

